WHEN to run WHAT (very important)
🟢 First time setup

Run: docker start jenkins

Step 2 (Docker install) 
Step 3 (run container)
🟢 Every time EC2 restarts

Run: docker ps

docker start jenkins
🟢 To check Jenkins running
docker ps
🟢 To restart Jenkins
docker restart jenkins
🟢 To stop Jenkins
docker stop jenkins

